author: Moerafaat
message:
Add `acosh` to XlaBuilder definitions in operation semantics list.

PiperOrigin-RevId: 808524440

files.patch: @@ -1591,6 +1591,8 @@ XlaBuilder supports these element-wise unary functions: `Cos(operand)` Element-wise cosine `x -> cos(x)`. +`Acosh(operand)` Element-wise inverse hyperbolic cosine `x -> acosh(x)`. + `Erf(operand)` Element-wise error function `x -> erf(x)` where $$\text{erf}(x) = \frac{2}{\sqrt{\pi}}\int_0^x e^{-t^2} \, dt$$. @@ -1667,6 +1669,9 @@ cbrt(x)`. `Cos(operand, result_accuracy)` Element-wise cosine `x -> cos(x)`. +`Acosh(operand, result_accuracy)` Element-wise inverse hyperbolic cosine +`x -> acosh(x)`. + `Erf(operand, result_accuracy)` Element-wise error function `x -> erf(x)` where
